{"tid":419411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（理性討論）你鐘意熟香蕉vs生香蕉？","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T04:59:57.000Z","uid":151161,"like":76,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9d153fb3e2f9c34a60ed06fab3d2dcf4bf641d38","tid":419411,"uid":151161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：熟咗嘅香蕉，金黃色嘅狀態。<br />\n<br />\n蕉皮透出細數嘅梅花點，隔住層蕉皮都聞到陣陣香蕉味，咬落口香甜軟熟，加埋朱古力真係無得輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205606_c9f0a190566ad1fae52c2f174c06e33b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205606_c9f0a190566ad1fae52c2f174c06e33b.jpg&h=0fba921c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205607_45fc323884f0cdd1caa047bdd8d8e402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205607_45fc323884f0cdd1caa047bdd8d8e402.jpg&h=2d774e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205354_c79d035d17973f52b8aef400a18843db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205354_c79d035d17973f52b8aef400a18843db.jpg&h=c8e3ae5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205355_3197ec2aa150864bc7abd475a5d0ed94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205355_3197ec2aa150864bc7abd475a5d0ed94.jpg&h=2f580a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：仲係生嘅香蕉，蕉皮仲係青bb 。<br />\n口感比較實淨，但就唔會太甜，有一陣淡淡嘅香蕉味，又健康啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205446_6a451500f6d66a685f603703c82163c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205446_6a451500f6d66a685f603703c82163c9.jpg&h=8d6246fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205447_c975f22b0fc440d2ec241b48e47d8045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205447_c975f22b0fc440d2ec241b48e47d8045.jpg&h=bbd5edbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205632_ca5e2d29cf67599de1c8281947bfae1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205632_ca5e2d29cf67599de1c8281947bfae1c.jpg&h=c5044eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/205632_a624547f26cead66279af3d3aecc3941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F205632_a624547f26cead66279af3d3aecc3941.jpg&h=d1e2c028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8916a53e5e4238ff1f2101932c97d47a386ec5a1","tid":419411,"uid":135694,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"半生熟"},{"pid":"016041e6c513e330c322cb6ebe0b9e989ad8a2dc","tid":419411,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"熟"},{"pid":"2c1c6d45b53b6aec6cab4e8ba236cc39dc76ab5f","tid":419411,"uid":104256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n食親都俾人話&quot;下 生嫁wo&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e5c8f55e4d957414a10a269a32dcfcc48410df","tid":419411,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":